294#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
295
296void SelectWithGesture::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(WebCore::IntPoint&&, WebKit::GestureType&&, WebKit::GestureRecognizerState&&, OptionSet<WebKit::SelectionFlags>&&)>&& completionHandler)
297{
298 std::optional<WebCore::IntPoint> point;
299 decoder >> point;
300 if (!point) {
301 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
302 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
303 return;
304 }
305 std::optional<WebKit::GestureType> gestureType;
306 decoder >> gestureType;
307 if (!gestureType) {
308 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
309 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
310 return;
311 }
312 std::optional<WebKit::GestureRecognizerState> gestureState;
313 decoder >> gestureState;
314 if (!gestureState) {
315 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
316 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
317 return;
318 }
319 std::optional<OptionSet<WebKit::SelectionFlags>> flags;
320 decoder >> flags;
321 if (!flags) {
322 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
323 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
324 return;
325 }
326 completionHandler(WTFMove(*point), WTFMove(*gestureType), WTFMove(*gestureState), WTFMove(*flags));
327}
328
329void SelectWithGesture::cancelReply(CompletionHandler<void(WebCore::IntPoint&&, WebKit::GestureType&&, WebKit::GestureRecognizerState&&, OptionSet<WebKit::SelectionFlags>&&)>&& completionHandler)
330{
331 completionHandler(IPC::AsyncReplyError<WebCore::IntPoint>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<WebKit::GestureType>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<WebKit::GestureRecognizerState>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<OptionSet<WebKit::SelectionFlags>>::create());
332}
333
334void SelectWithGesture::send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&& encoder, IPC::Connection& connection, const WebCore::IntPoint& point, WebKit::GestureType gestureType, WebKit::GestureRecognizerState gestureState, const OptionSet<WebKit::SelectionFlags>& flags)
335{
336 encoder.get() << point;
337 encoder.get() << gestureType;
338 encoder.get() << gestureState;
339 encoder.get() << flags;
340 connection.sendSyncReply(WTFMove(encoder));
341}

635
636void RequestDictationContext::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(String&&, String&&, String&&)>&& completionHandler)
637{
638 std::optional<String> selectedText;
639 decoder >> selectedText;
640 if (!selectedText) {
641 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
642 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
643 return;
644 }
645 std::optional<String> textBefore;
646 decoder >> textBefore;
647 if (!textBefore) {
648 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
649 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
650 return;
651 }
652 std::optional<String> textAfter;
653 decoder >> textAfter;
654 if (!textAfter) {
655 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
656 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
657 return;
658 }
659 completionHandler(WTFMove(*selectedText), WTFMove(*textBefore), WTFMove(*textAfter));
660}
661
662void RequestDictationContext::cancelReply(CompletionHandler<void(String&&, String&&, String&&)>&& completionHandler)
663{
664 completionHandler(IPC::AsyncReplyError<String>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<String>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<String>::create());
665}
666
667void RequestDictationContext::send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&& encoder, IPC::Connection& connection, const String& selectedText, const String& textBefore, const String& textAfter)
668{
669 encoder.get() << selectedText;
670 encoder.get() << textBefore;
671 encoder.get() << textAfter;
672 connection.sendSyncReply(WTFMove(encoder));
673}

799void GetSelectionContext::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(String&&, String&&, String&&)>&& completionHandler)
800{
801 std::optional<String> selectedText;
802 decoder >> selectedText;
803 if (!selectedText) {
804 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
805 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
806 return;
807 }
808 std::optional<String> textBefore;
809 decoder >> textBefore;
810 if (!textBefore) {
811 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
812 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
813 return;
814 }
815 std::optional<String> textAfter;
816 decoder >> textAfter;
817 if (!textAfter) {
818 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
819 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
820 return;
821 }
822 completionHandler(WTFMove(*selectedText), WTFMove(*textBefore), WTFMove(*textAfter));
823}

1379
1380void RunJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(IPC::DataReference&&, std::optional<WebCore::ExceptionDetails>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1381{
1382 std::optional<IPC::DataReference> resultData;
1383 decoder >> resultData;
1384 if (!resultData) {
1385 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1386 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1387 return;
1388 }
1389 std::optional<std::optional<WebCore::ExceptionDetails>> details;
1390 decoder >> details;
1391 if (!details) {
1392 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();

2771 completionHandler(WTFMove(*wasAppBound));
2772}
